dct_title_s: Topographic map of Salton Sea and vicinity
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours, spot heights, and bathymetric isolines.; Surveyed in 1925. Entire area mapped is below sea level.; Control by U.S. Geological Survey. Datum is mean sea level. North American datum.; 5000 yard grid based upon U.S. zone system, F.
dct_publisher_sm: Dept. of the Interior, U.S. Geological Survey (Washington, D.C)
